{"tid":1676927,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"加泰十萬人遊行中現黑紫荊旗 示威者望兩地分享策略 同爭公義自由","createTime":"2019-10-26T17:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T02:37:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"2af50bdae75f8adfa3c45c76d71ca609de48c0a3","tid":1676927,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cata-14_z8bfh_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcata-14_z8bfh_1200x0.png&h=a91f4662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加泰隆尼亞自治區首府巴塞隆拿今日有大型遊行，為八日內第二次發動人數以十萬計的示威，人潮從聖家堂沿瑪利娜大街 (Career de la Marina) 往海傍方向延綿數公里，當地警方稱有 35 萬人參與。遊行由獨派團體主辦，以「自由」為主題，抗議西班牙法院判處加泰自治政府官員及公投運動領袖九至十三年刑期。<br />\n<br />\n示威者 Ramon在遊行隊列中舉起香港示威常見的黑紫荊旗，與加泰旗並列，並寫上 Be Water, my friend. 他向《立場》記者表示，香港與加泰人民目前均受到打壓，自由被剝奪。他指自己一直有參與遊行，發聲反抗加泰人面對的不公義。他相信，香港、加泰及世界其他受壓迫地區的人民團結，彼此都可以變得更強大，繼續爭取公義與自由。<br />\n<br />\n他又說加泰人民非常支持香港，認為雙方可以分享策略，以爭取到自由與真正的民主。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/a5600273-9abf-4b3c-9d4d-2ba97eb3534020copy_0gS1P_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fa5600273-9abf-4b3c-9d4d-2ba97eb3534020copy_0gS1P_1200x0.png&h=3ed92b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-10-2720E4B88AE58D881.30.23_mOJ8y_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202019-10-2720E4B88AE58D881.30.23_mOJ8y_1200x0.png&h=dc58bb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/696d6700-43cb-49a3-b64d-483517e41181-120copy_BD4d9_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F696d6700-43cb-49a3-b64d-483517e